### Test v2 API with Conversation Awareness and Suggested Queries
### This file tests the fixes for:
### 1. v2 API returning incomplete responses
### 2. Suggested queries not appearing or being unnatural

### Test 1: Basic query to check v2 API works
POST {{host}}/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Hiển thị danh sách khách hàng"
}

### Test 2: Follow-up query to test conversation awareness
POST {{host}}/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Khách hàng nào ở Hà Nội?",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Test 3: Query to specifically test suggested queries
POST {{host}}/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Tổng doanh thu tháng này là bao nhiêu?"
}

### Test 4: Complex query to test suggestions quality
POST {{host}}/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Top 10 sản phẩm bán chạy nhất"
}

### Test 5: Conversation context test
POST {{host}}/api/v2/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Còn sản phẩm nào khác không?",
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}"
}

### Variables (replace with actual values)
@host = https://localhost:7001
@token = your_jwt_token_here
@connectionId = your_connection_id_here
@conversationId = conversation_id_from_previous_response